pageContext.claim: “Sleepy Joe Biden is the living embodiment of the corrupt political class that enriched himself while draining the economic life and soul from our country....For the last 47 years, Joe Biden, shipped away your jobs, shut down your factories, threw open your borders, and ravage our cities, while sacrificing American blood and treasure in endless and ridiculous foreign wars, in places you've never even heard of before, how ridiculous. He's a servant of the wealthy donors, globalists, and special interests who got rich bleeding America dry.”
pageContext.analysis: This is ridiculous over-the-top rhetoric, a smear on hyperdrive.
